dsmr-email-admin (1.0-1) trixie; urgency=low

  * Initial release.  Health-check and repair tool for the DSMR
    qmail/vpopmail/dovecot stack.  'check' runs a read-only audit; 'fix'
    repairs stale control/config left by create-if-absent postinsts (a low
    qmail softlimit, swapped vpopmail.pgsql password/database fields, a
    dovecot SQL conf out of sync with vpopmail.pgsql, and a stopped vpopmail
    PostgreSQL cluster); 'selftest' proves delivery and dovecot auth end to
    end with a throwaway vpopmail mailbox.

